<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: blue; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: white;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;"><strong>12:20|Wilhelm:</strong> 我想我会试试的</span></span><br />
